<p>Blue, green, or violet lights outline objects inside a 20-foot <a href="/wiki/Magic#Area_of_Effect" title="Magic">cube</a> of space. All <a href="/wiki/Creature" title="Creature">creatures</a> in the area make a <a href="/wiki/Dexterity" title="Dexterity" class="mw-redirect">Dexterity</a> save or be cast in light as well. The light cast by this spell illuminates a 10-foot radius.
</p><p>Attacks against affected creatures are made with <a href="/wiki/How_to_Play#Advantage_and_Disadvantage" title="How to Play">advantage</a>, and affected creature or object (if applicable) will no longer be <a href="/wiki/Conditions#Invisible" title="Conditions">invisible</a>.
</p>
